Package: EcoCleanR
Title: Tools for Cleaning Occurrence Data to Generate Species Biogeographic Ranges
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Priyanka", "Soni", , "sonip@usc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool to integrate biodiversity data from multiple aggregators and offers a step-by-step framework for data cleaning, outlier detection, and the generation of species biogeographic ranges. It also supports the extraction of relevant environmental information to assist in ecological and biogeographic analyses.
